dc_title_s: Northern Lancaster County Groundwater Study: Pennsylvania
dc_description_s: Contains various shapefiles, pdf's, and jpeg maps pertaining to the Northern Lancaster County Groundwater study. Layer include groundwater basin shapefiles include - river basins, MCD's, census blocks, sewage treatment outfalls, water use, study area, dry stream valley systems, geology, karst modified uplands, impervious surfaces, wetlands. JPEG maps include study area, basins, withdraws, conductivity, nitrates, geology, water tables, flowlines, mapplate.
